data.description: Woodlawn Community is an established neighborhood located along the Intracoastal Waterway & is located by the Hathaway Bridge which is considered the gateway to Panama City Beach. This home has been completely renovated from the roof in 2019 to the hot water heater, New wall to wall Shaw Floorte LTV flooring.  New cabinetry with Venatino White Quartz countertops have been replaced in the kitchen and master bathroom. The kitchen features new stainless appliances. Other upgrades include a new hot water heater, windows, & light fixtures throughout the home. The master bedroom was reconfigured during the remodeling to open up the floor plan & enlarge the master bathroom & walk in closet space with dual entry from the laundry room to the master master suite.
